Where Food Comes From Inc.
 
www.wherefoodcomesfrom.com | (866) 395-5883
Where Food Comes From, Inc. (WFCF, ICS, IMI) offers a wide array of verification and certification services to help food producers, brands and consumers differentiate certain attributes and production methods in the marketplace. WFCF is an independent, third-party auditing company recognized and utilized by numerous standard-setting bodies as an accredited verification or certification service provider, doing business through three distinct corporate divisions: IMI Global, International Certification Services, and Validus Verification Services. Our mission is to provide valuable and authentic verification services to the food industry while also facilitating consumer discovery and choice around the food they eat. Learn more at www.wherefoodcomesfrom.com.
