Where Food Comes From, Inc.




Where Food Comes From, Inc. is the leading supplier of certification and verification services to the food industry.  If you want to tell or learn the story of where and how your food is produced, Where Food Comes From does just that!  As part of a collaborative partnership to expand opportunities and services available to certification customers, Where Food Comes From, Inc. purchased ICS in 2012.  Now more than ever, ICS customers have an opportunity to make the most of their Organic or Gluten-Free certification process.  Where Food Comes From offers distinct company Divisions, each specializing in a specific area of certification expertise.  As a result, ICS customers can now look at ways to combine additional programs or standards with their Organic certification - and it can all be done under one roof! Learn more about Where Food Comes from at www.wherefoodcomesfrom.com




Where Food Comes From Featured Producers

Where Food Comes From is dedicated to connecting consumers to the people and families that produce their food.  As a part of this mission, every supplier approved through any of the Where Food Comes From accredited certifiers is automatically eligible for the Where Food Comes From Source Verification program.  This not only adds them to the list of approved suppliers for product or brands utilizing the Where Food Comes From® label and QR Code, but also provides the opportunity for that location to submit a Family Profile to be featured on the WhereFoodComesFrom.com website. Download the Family Profile form here




International Certification Services, Inc. (ICS) PO Box 517, 301 5th Ave SE Medina, ND 58467 United States ​Tel: 701-486-3578 * Fax: 701-486-3580 * email: info@ics-intl.com























































